{"tid":1506633,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【一場自編自導自演的開槍事件！】","createTime":"2019-08-26T00:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T01:28:04.000Z","uid":259753,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8c499d5ed153eeab7edc1078aa7bedd0399e421e","tid":1506633,"uid":259753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:54:01.000Z","msg":"【一場自編自導自演的開槍事件！】<br />\n<br />\n點解會有班示威者，全部身上有方形螢光粉紅標記，主動攻擊警車，勇武到過晒龍嘅？<br />\n<br />\n事發後，有位警司對班記者話 : 你哋應該欣賞同事嘅英勇....可能係講呢班方形螢光粉紅標記嘅喬裝示威者喎！<br />\n<br />\n以下內容係轉載，無辦法 Fact check，就當有朋友發開口夢啦！<br />\n==================================<br />\n//我有個喺地鐵做嘅中學同學， 講咗啲佢昨日親眼見嘅嘢畀我聽：<br />\n<br />\n大約10點開始，九龍灣車廠有約30多架警車入內，全部泊晒禁區，所以唔會有傳媒知。<br />\n<br />\n當我食飯，落到去車廠飯堂，入面幾乎坐滿，目測都有過百嘅警員「扮示威者」，全身full gear黑衫，其中同事目擊到當中一個「扮示威者」嘅警員打開袋，入面有可樂瓶裝住透明液體，相信係燃燒彈。<br />\n<br />\n噚日，我見到呢種情境，真係好想遞信辭職。<br />\n====================================<br />\n<br />\n粉紅標記的喬裝示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/610134032376863/posts/2606639059393007/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F610134032376863%2Fposts%2F2606639059393007%2F&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxreFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=563c7645\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/610134032376863/posts/2606639059393007/</a><br />\n<br />\n警員竟可自己揸走架載滿鐵通嘅的士 : <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/109140177111638/posts/119728816052774/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F109140177111638%2Fposts%2F119728816052774%2F&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxreFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=a02a66b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/109140177111638/posts/119728816052774/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RX5SkNp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRX5SkNp.jpg&h=3e831347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z11mYy5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ11mYy5.jpg&h=ba8db535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/maKPn0M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmaKPn0M.jpg&h=d734a586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QXEjLd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQXEjLd7.jpg&h=ac891991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩FB見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1be877e71577d61270b29d4a52963386a5e8d77","tid":1506633,"uid":14202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:00:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5195f29b5163e8aeaab839b12a9871e7c75e96f","tid":1506633,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:04:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4e53dbc905dc948a8d53d600b24b42f03c3b3f","tid":1506633,"uid":16922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:09:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64918c1fde367b178e014e58eb1ae8348b77da6d","tid":1506633,"uid":153588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:11:43.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b773e569ba711b27706bdae64f2d4ab1f89f40cb","tid":1506633,"uid":7832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:11:54.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"bf184813ba4835eb2ece1f72038c5ae3cf89a8b2","tid":1506633,"uid":150420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:13:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2f3c8143ecda2755d8f94eec0f418802627125c","tid":1506633,"uid":275616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:13:5